-- Andreae-Noris Zahn Proposes CFO Ralf Lieb as New CEO, FTD Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-02-23T18:32:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-23/andreae-noris-zahn-proposes-cfo-ralf-lieb-as-new-ceo-ftd-says.html
Andreae-Noris Zahn AG (ANZ) ,  Germany ’s
third-largest drug wholesaler, plans to make Chief Financial
Officer Ralf Lieb the company’s new chief executive officer in
August 2013, when chief executive Thomas Truemper retires,
 Financial Times Deutschland  reported in a preview of an article
that will run tomorrow, without saying where it got the
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  